  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_014_000017",
    "sentence": "[ 22 ] 自鴈門以東，盡遼陽，為燕、代。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_014_000018",
    "sentence": "[ 23 ] 常山以南，太行左轉，度河、濟，漸于海，為齊、趙。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_014_000019",
    "sentence": "[ 24 ] 穀、泗以往，奄有龜、蒙，為梁、楚。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_014_000020",
    "sentence": "[ 25 ] 東帶江、湖，薄會稽，為荊吳。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_014_000021",
    "sentence": "[ 26 ] 北界淮瀕，略廬、衡，為淮南。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_014_000022",
